00:41.751 --> 00:43.751
<i> I also have two kids, a wife,</i>
<i> two dogs,</i>

00:43.794 --> 00:45.753
and some chickens, so...

00:45.796 --> 00:49.048
<i> - I'm Harlan Whitman, and I've</i>
<i>been forging knives since 2002.</i>

00:49.091 --> 00:50.841
I am a goofy person.

00:50.885 --> 00:53.594
