07:25.737 --> 07:28.113
<i> So I have to improvise.</i>

07:28.157 --> 07:30.490
I was a little short
on the length.

07:30.534 --> 07:32.576
Basically, changing the design
to another sword

07:32.619 --> 07:34.244
