07:34.288 --> 07:35.787
<i> I realize I don't have enough,</i>
<i> so I need</i>

07:35.831 --> 07:37.247
<i> to go into where that guard is</i>

07:37.291 --> 07:39.332
<i> and do a guardless sword.</i>

