07:41.837 --> 07:43.420
<i> It's not what I</i>
<i> really wanted to do,</i>

07:43.464 --> 07:46.590
<i> but it's a cool-looking</i>
<i> post-apocalyptic weapon,</i>

07:46.633 --> 07:49.009
<i> and I know that I can fix it</i>
<i> on the grinder.</i>

07:49.052 --> 07:51.261
