08:24.671 --> 08:28.965
<i>- I'm going to make really big,</i>
<i> scooped serrations,</i>

08:29.009 --> 08:30.800
and it just looks cool.

08:30.844 --> 08:32.636
- Shazam.
Look at that.

08:32.679 --> 08:34.387
- Huge serrations.

08:34.431 --> 08:36.139
- So I always think of
serrations as, like,

08:36.183 --> 08:37.557
fangs on something.

