23:26.572 --> 23:28.322
that I've done so far.

23:28.366 --> 23:29.615
- Thank you.

23:29.659 --> 23:30.783
- Eric, ready?

23:30.827 --> 23:32.576
- Absolutely, sir.

23:32.620 --> 23:39.583
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

23:40.628 --> 23:42.711
[ice shattering]

23:42.755 --> 23:49.760
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

23:49.804 --> 23:52.638
- [laughing]

