around a little bit.

24:00.940 --> 24:03.774
However, you have enough
weight in the blade

24:03.818 --> 24:05.025
that as I'm chopping,

24:05.069 --> 24:06.902
I mean, it just--it wants to go.

24:06.946 --> 24:08.320
That's where it wants to be.

24:08.364 --> 24:10.114
It wants to get into that ice
