<i> [rock music]</i>

24:49.405 --> 24:50.154
<i> [rock music]</i>

24:50.198 --> 24:53.574
<i> [suspenseful music]</i>

24:53.618 --> 24:54.700
[ice shattering]

24:54.744 --> 24:56.952
