<i> ♪ ♪</i>

25:04.086 --> 25:05.711
<i> - Watching the blade snap,</i>
<i> you definitely feel</i>

25:05.755 --> 25:07.171
<i> your stomach kind of sink</i>
<i> down a little bit.</i>

