25:27.527 --> 25:29.693
- Thank you, guys.

25:29.737 --> 25:31.320
<i> It's a little frustrating</i>

25:31.364 --> 25:33.239
<i> knowing that I can't finish</i>
<i> to the end.</i>

25:33.282 --> 25:34.865
<i> But it's just the end</i>
<i> of this experience.</i>

25:34.909 --> 25:36.033
<i> I've got plenty more to do.</i>

25:36.077 --> 25:37.618
I'll be smithing at home again.

25:37.662 --> 25:39.703
