30:34.208 --> 30:37.626
<i> and I realize...</i>

30:37.670 --> 30:39.002
I need a quench tank.

30:39.046 --> 30:40.546
Oh, [bleep].

30:40.589 --> 30:41.839
<i> I don't have</i>
<i> a quench tank big enough</i>

30:41.882 --> 30:43.507
<i> to quench this thing.</i>

30:43.551 --> 30:45.133
Yeah, I wasn't
quite expecting that.

30:45.177 --> 30:47.302
<i> I have been so thorough</i>
<i> with my measurements,</i>

30:47.346 --> 30:48.679
<i> and the one thing I forget</i>

30:48.722 --> 30:50.389
