30:50.432 --> 30:52.432
Nope.

30:52.476 --> 30:54.101
<i> I've got a pretty substantial</i>
<i> junk pile in my backyard.</i>

30:54.144 --> 30:55.602
<i> Hopefully I got</i>
<i> something back there.</i>

30:55.646 --> 30:56.728
Plastic.

30:56.772 --> 30:58.021
Yeah, to put it mildly, yo,

30:58.065 --> 30:59.606
I'm a little freaked out
