30:59.650 --> 31:00.607
<i> I got nothing to quench</i>
<i> this thing in.</i>

31:00.651 --> 31:01.650
[bleep].

31:01.694 --> 31:02.943
<i> [rock music]</i>

31:06.407 --> 31:07.781
<i> [rock music]</i>

31:07.825 --> 31:09.157
<i> - I'm a little</i>
<i> freaked out right now.</i>

31:09.201 --> 31:11.243
<i> I got nothing to quench</i>
<i> this thing in.</i>

31:11.287 --> 31:13.704
<i> I've got a pretty substantial</i>
<i> junk pile in my backyard.</i>

31:13.747 --> 31:16.415
So hopefully
I got something back there.

31:16.458 --> 31:17.749
Nope.

31:17.793 --> 31:19.835
That would work,
but it's plastic.

31:19.879 --> 31:21.503
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

31:21.547 --> 31:23.297
I think this'll work.

31:23.340 --> 31:24.965
<i> Perfect.</i>
<i> Grabbing the angle grinder.</i>

31:25.009 --> 31:26.675
<i> I'm cutting this thing</i>
<i> right down the center.</i>

31:26.719 --> 31:30.178
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:30.222 --> 31:31.013
It'll work.

31:31.056 --> 31:32.514
That was a little stressful,

31:32.558 --> 31:34.224
<i> and I'm genuinely</i>

31:34.268 --> 31:36.143
<i> getting a little nervous</i>
<i> around this quench.</i>

31:36.186 --> 31:38.186
<i> This is a pivotal moment</i>
<i> in this whole construction.</i>

31:38.230 --> 31:39.563
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:39.607 --> 31:40.814
So I'm just trying
to get some heat

31:40.858 --> 31:42.608
into that section real good.

31:42.651 --> 31:44.735
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:44.778 --> 31:46.320
Okay.

31:46.363 --> 31:53.368
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:53.412 --> 31:54.870
Oh, my goodness.

31:54.914 --> 31:57.581
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:57.625 --> 31:59.499
Straight as a [bleep] arrow.

31:59.543 --> 32:03.378
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

32:03.422 --> 32:05.380
<i> - It's day three.</i>
<i> I'm a little sore,</i>

