32:14.934 --> 32:16.391
Now it's time
for the heat treat.

32:16.435 --> 32:18.060
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

32:18.103 --> 32:20.395
Everything leading up
to this point is just critical.

32:20.439 --> 32:22.856
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

32:22.900 --> 32:24.483
All right.
Here we go.

32:24.526 --> 32:28.946
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

32:28.989 --> 32:31.615
Beautiful.

32:31.659 --> 32:34.910
<i> I was totally giddy when</i>
